Package: ARBO
Type: Package
Title: Rapid Spatial Clustering and Enriched Metabolite Discovery for MSI Data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Xinyin Deng", email = "2386180950@qq.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for preprocessing, visualization, spatial clustering,
    and enriched metabolite screening for mass spectrometry imaging (MSI)
    metabolomics data. The package supports Python-based UMAP embedding
    through 'reticulate', multiple clustering methods, MSI image
    reconstruction and overlay, and integration of clustering results into
    Cardinal MSI objects. Supported UMAP input strategies include direct
    min-max scaled spectra and row-wise L2-normalized PCA scores computed
    with 'irlba'.
